 makes accessible certain Oriental, and especially Indian, source material hitherto almost unknown to students.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aAestheticsxHistory. 0aArtxPhilosophyxHistory. 0aArt, Asian. 0aArt, Indic. 0aArt. 0aKünste, Bildende Kunst allgemein. 0aKünste, Bildende Kunst allgemein. 4aAesthetics -- History. 4aArt -- Philosophy -- History. 4aArt, Asian. 4aArt, Indic. 4aNature (Aesthetics). 7aART / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP e-dition: Art & Architecture eBook Packagez9783110353471oZDB-23-HAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP e-dition: Complete eBook Packagez9783110353488oZDB-23-HCO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z97831104422120 cprintz978067428291940uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/harvard.978067428386240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674283862423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780674283862.jpg  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_AD  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-HAA  aZDB-23-HCO